➜我爱我的家乡——​“榆林抗硬”融媒大直播圆满结束
http://www.sohu.com/a/438066335_355330	30412
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>榆林的美丽，美在风景。</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>榆林的美</span></strong><strong><span>丽，美在历史。</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>榆林的美丽，美在人文。</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>榆林的美丽，美在物产。</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>榆林的美丽，美在前景</span></strong><strong><span>。</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img height="" width="100%" src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201214/df158890e9274f2ab951cd70014bc20f.jpeg" /></p>
